name: ax-wl-11v
params: setvar s0, setvar s1, wff w0
body: |- wi(wal(s0, wal(s1, w0)), wal(s1, wal(s0, w0)))
comment: Version of ~ ax-11 with distinct variable conditions. Currently implemented as an axiom to detect unintended references to the foundational axiom ~ ax-11 . It will later be converted into a theorem directly based on ~ ax-11 . (Contributed by Wolf Lammen, 28-Jun-2019.)
